Package: kvkapiR
Title: Interface to the Dutch Chamber of Commerce (KvK) API
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Coen", "Eisma", , "coeneisma@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-9001-2572"))
Description: Access business registration data from the Dutch Chamber of 
    Commerce (Kamer van Koophandel, KvK) through their official API. Search 
    for companies by name, location, or registration number. Retrieve detailed 
    business profiles, establishment information, and company name histories. 
    Built on 'httr2' for robust API interaction with automatic pagination, 
    error handling, and usage tracking.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
